	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Action</strong> - 20 ft. Radius (150 ft) - 8th Level (Conjuration) - VS - Concentration (Up to 1 Minute)</p><p><strong>[[/save DEX]]{Dexterity Save}</strong></p><p>The cloud spreads around corners and the area is &amp;reference[Heavily Obscured].</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Area Hazard:</strong> The area covered by the wall is &amp;reference[obscuredheavily]. Targets roll a save when they enter or when they end their turn in the wall (but only once per turn).</p></li><li><p><strong>Concentration:</strong> At the start of each of your turns, the cloud moves 10 ft. directly away from you in a direction you choose.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><em>The cloud can be dispersed by a moderate or stronger wind (at least 10 mph).</em></p>",
